		<fdd:description>QuickTime file format that wraps an Apple ProRes 4444 and Apple ProRes 4444 XQ codec video bitstreams with other data chunks, e.g., audio.  </fdd:description>
		<fdd:shortDescription>QuickTime wrapper with Apple ProRes 4444 and Apple ProRes 4444 XQ codec video bitstreams and other data chunks, e.g., audio. </fdd:shortDescription>
