			<p>
				<b>Accessibility Features</b>
			</p>
			<p>See <fddLink id="fdd000527">Apple ProRes 444</fddLink>  and <fddLink id="fdd000052">QuickTime</fddLink> for web accessibility information related to this codec and its most common container format.</p>
			<p>See <a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/media/av/">W3C's Making Audio and Video Media Accessible</a> for more general information about accessible sound and moving image media.</p>
		</fdd:selfDocumentation>
		<fdd:externalDependencies>See <fddLink id="fdd000052">QuickTime</fddLink>
		</fdd:externalDependencies>
